Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.10,0:18:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Baiklah, kalau begitu biar kupikirkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.32,0:18:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wajah kalian terlihat asing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.25,0:18:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.38,0:18:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Badanmu besar sekali, berapa usiamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.11,0:18:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Aku 9 tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.88,0:18:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sembilan tahun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.59,0:18:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Bohong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.59,0:18:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Dasar, monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.51,0:18:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakit sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.02,0:18:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hentikan!
